mal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">3. </span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-weight:="" 700;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">Правила формирования</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">: </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-left: 8.5pt; text-align: justify; margin-top: 6pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">a. Контроль действующих договоров Специалиста с Подписантом. При наличии действующего Договора новый Договор физического лица не оформляется;</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-left: 8.5pt; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">b. Специалист должен пройти до Шага 4 Блока Оформление.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; text-align: justify; margin-top: 6pt; margin-bottom: 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">4. </span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-weight:="" 700;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">Наименование файла</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">: </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-left: 8.5pt; text-align: justify; margin-top: 6pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">xxxxx-yyyyyy-zzz, </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-left: 8.5pt; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">где </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-left: 8.5pt; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">xxxxxx – код контрагента в 1С, который указывается в реквизите Контрагент Документа Дополнительное соглашение, </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-left: 8.5pt; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">yyyyyy – код физлица в 1С, который указывается в реквизите Физлицо Документа Дополнительное соглашение, </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-left: 8.5pt; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background