="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">)</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">Телефон (канал связи): </span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">     </span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-weight:="" 700;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">§ IХ.2. Договор самозанятый</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">1. </span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-weight:="" 700;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">Инициирование</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">: после нажатия кнопки </span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-weight:="" 700;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">Согласовать</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"=""> </span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-style:="" italic;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">[Заявку]</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"=""> в интерфейсе Супервайзера, Проект-менеджера; Специалист с налоговым статусом самозанятый; автоматически</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">2. </span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-weight:="" 700;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">Подписант</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">: определяется по значению реквизита Организация Справочника Проекты по значению реквизита Проект; используются все значения </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">3. </span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-weight:="" 700;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">Правила формирования</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">: </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-left: 8.5pt; text-align: justify; margin-top: 6pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">a. Контроль действующих договоров Специалиста с Подписантом. При наличии действующего Договора новый Договор не оформляется;</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-left: 8.5pt; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">b. Специалист должен пройти до Шага 4 Блока Оформление.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-left: 8.5pt; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">c. При наличии действующего или ранее действующего договора физического лица с организацией новый договор как с самозанятым не заключается в течение 2 лет с момента расторжения договора физического лица.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; text-align: justify; margin-top: 6pt; margin-bottom: 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">4. </span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-weight:="" 700;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">Наименование файла</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">: </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-left: 8.5pt; text-align: justify; margin-top: 6pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">xxxxx-yyyyyy-zz, </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-left: 8.5pt; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">где </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-left: 8.5pt; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">xxxxxx – код контрагента в 1С, который указывается в реквизите Заказчик Документа Договор самозанятого, </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-left: 8.5pt; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">yyyyyy – код физлица в 1С, который указывается в реквизите Самозанятый Документа Договор самозанятого, </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-left: 8.5pt; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">zzz – порядковый номер Документа Договор самозанятого, оформляемого между Заказчиком и Самозанятым, начинается с 01 для каждой Организации, по которой оформляется Документ Договор самозанятого</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; text-align: justify; margin-top: 6pt; margin-bottom: 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">5. </span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-weight:="" 700;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-va