r:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"=""> - не более ₽     </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"=""> за 1 день. </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-left: 8.5pt;text-align: justify;margin-top:6pt;margin-bottom:6pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">9.3.</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"=""> Арендная плата Исполнителю за предоставление Исполнителем собственного и/или управляемого по доверенности транспортного средства: модель      </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"=""> регистрационный знак      </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"=""> - не более ₽     </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"=""> за 1 день.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:6pt;margin-bottom:6pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">10. Дата начала оказания услуг:      </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:6pt;margin-bottom:6pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">11. Дата окончания оказания услуг:      </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:6pt;margin-bottom:6pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">12. Задание обязательно для согласования Сторонами любым из способов, определенных Договором.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:6pt;margin-bottom:6pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">13. В период действия Задания Заказчик и/или его уполномоченные представители вправе уточнять/корректировать фактически требуемые объемы услуг (не ниже минимальных объемов), интервалы и места их оказания путем направления уведомлений по каналам связи в адрес Исполнителя. Уточнения/корректировки вступают в силу для обеих Сторон при наличии соответствующих конклюдентных действий Исполнителя. Изменения в Задании фиксируются при сдаче-приёмке услуг по Заданию.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:6pt;margin-bottom:6pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">14. Исполнитель обязуется самостоятельно ознакомиться с локальными актами, регламентирующими порядок оказания услуг в конкретном месте проведения, а также самостоятельно взаимодействовать с администрацией места проведения по любым вопросам, влияющим на комплектность, качество и своевременность оказываемых Заказчику услуг по Заданию.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:6pt;margin-bottom:6pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">15. Сдача-приёмка услуг по Заданию, а также их оплата Заказчиком производится в соответствии с условиями Договора.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:6pt;margin-bottom:6pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">16. Задание оформлено в 2 (Двух) экземплярах, имеющих одинаковую юридическую силу, по 1 (Одному) экземпляру для каждой Стороны.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:6pt;margin-bottom:6pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">17. Подписи Сторон:</span></p><div dir="ltr" style="margin-left:0pt;" align="left"><table style="border: none;"><colgroup><col width="203"><col width="421"></colgroup><tbody><tr style="height:0pt"><td style="vertical-align:top;padding:0pt 5.75pt 0pt 5.75pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:6pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-weight:="" 700;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">Заказчик:</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:6pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">     </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"=""> _________(     </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">)</span></p><br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:6pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">м.п.</span></p></td><td style="vertical-align:top;padding:0pt 5.75pt 0pt 5.75pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:6pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-weight:="" 700;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">Исполнитель:</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:6pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">______________ (     </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">)</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">Телефон (канал связи):      </span></p><br></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-weight:="" 700;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">§ IХ.7. Задание самозанятого</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">1. </span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-weight:="" 700;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">Инициирование</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">: после нажатия кнопки </span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-weight:="" 700;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">Согласовать</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"=""> </span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-style:="" italic;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">[Заявку]</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"=""> в интерфейсе Супервайзера, Проект-менеджера; Специалист с налоговым статусом физическое лицо; автоматически</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">2. </span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-weight:="" 700;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">Подписант</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">: определяется по значению реквизита Организация Справочника Проекты по значению реквизита Проект; используются все значения </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">3. </span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-weight:="" 700;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">Правила формирования</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">: </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-left: 8.5pt; text-align: justify; margin-top: 6pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">a. Привязка к действующему Договору самозанятого с организацией;</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-left: 8.5pt; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">b. Специалист должен пройти до Шага 4 Блока Оформление.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; text-align: justify; margin-top: 6pt; margin-bottom: 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">4. </span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-weight:="" 700;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">Наименование файла</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">: </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-left: 8.5pt; text-align: justify; margin-top: 6pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">xxxxx-yyyyyy-zzz-wwww </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-left: 8.5pt; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">где </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-left: 8.5pt; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">xxxxxx – код контрагента в 1С, который указывается в реквизите Контрагент Документа Договор самозанятого, </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-left: 8.5pt; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">yyyyyy – код физлица в 1С, который указывается в реквизите Физлицо Документа Договор самозанятого, </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-left: 8.5pt; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-fami