" times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"=""> модель      </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"=""> идентификационный номер      </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"=""> - ₽     </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">. </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-left: 8.5pt;text-align: justify;margin-top:6pt;margin-bottom:6pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">6.3.</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"=""> Арендная плата Исполнителю за предоставление Исполнителем собственного и/или управляемого по доверенности транспортного средства: модель      </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"=""> регистрационный знак      </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"=""> - ₽     </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:6pt;margin-bottom:6pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">7. Согласно условиям Договора Заказчик обязан оплатить вознаграждение Исполнителя не позднее 10 (Десяти) рабочих дней со дня подписания Сторонами Акта.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:6pt;margin-bottom:6pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">8. Согласно условиям Договора Заказчик обязан исполнить прочие денежные обязательства перед Исполнителем при их наличии в течение 15 (Пятнадцати) рабочих дней со дня подписания Сторонами Акта.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">9. Актом подтверждается полное выполнение Сторонами своих обязательств за указанный период по Заданию      -     -     </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">-     </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"=""> от      </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"=""> г. к Договору присоединения №     -     -     </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"=""> от      </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">г. к Договору-оферте №     </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"=""> в редакции от      </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"=""> г. Стороны взаимных претензий друг к другу не имеют.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:6pt;margin-bottom:6pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">10. Акт оформлен в 2 (Двух) экземплярах, имеющих одинаковую юридическую силу, по 1 (Одному) экземпляру для каждой Стороны.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:6pt;margin-bottom:6pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-position:="" font-variant-emoji:="" vertical-align:="" baseline;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">11. Подписи Сторон:</span></p><div dir="ltr" style="margin-left:0pt;" align="left"><table style="border: none;"><colgroup><col width="203"><col width="421"></colgroup><tbody><tr style="height:0pt"><td style="vertical-align:top;padding:0pt 5.75pt 0pt 5.75pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:6pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: " times="" new="" roman",="" serif;="" color:="" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" background-color:="" transparent;="" font-weight:="" 700;="" font-variant-numeric:="" normal;="" font-variant-east-asian:="" font-variant-alternates:="" font-variant-